Correlation Class¶

In [3]:
class  Correlation ():
    def __init__(self):
        albums=pd.read_csv('albums.csv')
        songs=pd.read_csv('songs.csv')
        users=pd.read_csv('users.csv')
        usersongrelationships=pd.read_csv('usersongrelationships.csv')
        df1=pd.merge(songs, albums, on="album_id") 
        df2=pd.merge(df1,usersongrelationships, on="song_id") 
        df=pd.merge(df2, users, on="user_id") 
        self.df=df

    def users(self,username):
        self.user_mat=self.df.pivot_table(index='song_title',columns='username',values='listen_count')
        user=self.user_mat[username]
        user_corr=pd.DataFrame(self.user_mat.corrwith(user,drop=True),columns=['Correlation'])
        user_corr.fillna(0,inplace=True)
        user_corr=pd.DataFrame(user_corr['Correlation'].sort_values()[::-1],columns=['Correlation'])

        #removing the items whoes corelation is less than 0
        self.user_corr=user_corr[user_corr['Correlation']>0]

    def songs(self,song_title):
        self.song_mat=self.df.pivot_table(index='username',columns='song_title',values='listen_count')
        song=self.song_mat[song_title]
        song_corr=pd.DataFrame(self.song_mat.corrwith(song,drop=True),columns=['Correlation'])
        song_corr.fillna(0,inplace=True)
        song_corr=pd.DataFrame(song_corr['Correlation'].sort_values()[::-1],columns=['Correlation'])

        #removing the items whoes corelation is less than 0
        self.song_corr=song_corr[song_corr['Correlation']>0]

    def albums(self,album_title):
        self.album_mat=self.df.pivot_table(index='username',columns='album_title',values='listen_count', aggfunc='sum')
        album=self.album_mat[album_title]
        album_corr=pd.DataFrame(self.album_mat.corrwith(album,drop=True),columns=['Correlation'])
        album_corr.fillna(0,inplace=True)
        album_corr=pd.DataFrame(album_corr['Correlation'].sort_values()[::-1],columns=['Correlation'])

        #removing the items whoes corelation is less than 0
        self.album_corr=album_corr[album_corr['Correlation']>0]
